title: PSR Discography (mp3 192kbps) (experimental ambient)
description:
This is a full discography of the experimental ambient group "PSR" from Champaign-Urbana, Illinois.  All files are mp3 192kpbs, with the exception of one album which is slightly lower bitrate (140-160ish).  Uploaded and seeded with permission from the band.

PSR is known for their improvised experimental ambient compositions, ranging from watery and soothing to maddeningly psychedelic.  Many of the albums were recorded as straight-through improvisations.  More information on the band can be found at their website: <a href=" http://psr47.com" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW"> http://psr47.com</a>


Album Listing:

- On Illuminating The Lands Of The Ten Directions  (2004)
- End Of An Era  (2004)
- Ethereal Ephemera  (2004)
- 47 Eridani  (2004)
- 810101  (2004)
- Kairos  (2005)
- WEFT Sessions  (2005) (live FM radio performance)
- Asymptotic  (2006)
- Post Meridiem  (2007)
- Remixes
